<div class="body" id="fhbody-174387867">
	
		
	

	
		
		<div id="text-174387867" class="p">
			
		 	
				Amazon's Kindle e-reader system is <a href="https://goodereader.com/blog/kindle/amazon-kindle-will-not-download-books-to-the-e-reader">experiencing a widespread outage</a>, affecting new book downloads and access to undownloaded titles in users' libraries. The issue, confirmed by Amazon support, is expected to last at least 48 hours.<br>
		 	
		</div>

		

		

		
			
		
